briefTitle: Discordant Hormonal Status of Breast Cancer.
officialTitle: Discordant Hormonal Status Between Primary Tumor and Axillary Lymph Node in Breast Cancer Patients.
primaryOutcomeMeasure: Association of hormonal status between primary breast tumor and axillary lymph nodes
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Breast cancer patients stage I,II and III with axillary lymph nodes metastasis.

Exclusion Criteria:

* Breast cancer patients stage I,II and III without axillary lymph nodes metastasis.
